---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service | Obsidian Plugins Guide" description="Terms of Service for Obsidian Plugins Guide." canonicalURL="https://notes-automate.com/terms/">
  <article class="policy-page">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="lead">These terms explain how you may use Obsidian Plugins Guide and the practical limits of our editorial guides.</p>
    <h2>Use of the site</h2>
    <p>Obsidian Plugins Guide publishes informational articles about Obsidian plugins, note automation, PKM workflows, templates, and privacy-minded knowledge systems. The content is provided for general education and comparison research. It is not legal, medical, financial, safety, or professional engineering advice.</p>
    <h2>Editorial independence</h2>
    <p>We aim to keep reviews, comparisons, and recommendations useful for readers first. We may update, remove, or correct content when products change, links break, or better evidence becomes available.</p>
    <h2>External links and affiliate links</h2>
    <p>Some articles link to third-party websites, tools, marketplaces, or affiliate programs. We do not control those external services and are not responsible for their pricing, claims, availability, data practices, or support.</p>
    <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Do not scrape, republish, or resell our articles at scale without written permission.</li>
      <li>Do not use the site in a way that disrupts hosting, analytics, advertising, or security systems.</li>
      <li>Do not misrepresent our recommendations as paid endorsements unless a page explicitly says so.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about these terms can be sent to <a href="mailto:hello@notes-automate.com">hello@notes-automate.com</a>.</p>
    <p>Last updated: May 10, 2026.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .policy-page { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem; line-height: 1.75; }
  .policy-page h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
  .policy-page .lead { color: #4b5563; font-size: 1.08rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .policy-page h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 2rem 0 .75rem; }
  .policy-page ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; }
  .policy-page li { margin-bottom: .55rem; }
  .policy-page a { color: var(--accent, #2563eb); text-decoration: underline; }
</style>

